des:
BanlanX help you to control your LED light nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to change the LED's on/off, color, brightness.

After connecting Alexa to your BanlanX products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "BanlanX" app from Google play or App store;
(2) Register one BanlanX account in our "BanlanX" app;
(3) You need to have: some BanlanX devices in hand;
(5) Download "Amazon Alexa" app from android,ios or mazon app market
(6) Configure Echo with "Amazon Alexa" app;
(7) Search "BanlanX" skill from the "Amazon Alexa" app "Skills & Games" category;
(8) Click "ENABLE TO USE" on the "BanlanX" skill page, and you'll be navigated to BanlanX login page;
(9) Input your BanlanX account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10) Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your LED light like these:
"Alexa, turn on the living room light."
"Alexa, turn off the living room light."
"Alexa, set the living room light color to red."
"Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent."
"Alexa, dim the living room light by 25 percent."
...
